# Data Sources

## Philadelphia Organizations and Programs Referenced

This document lists every Philadelphia organization, city program, and civic resource referenced or recommended by the Climate Civic Action Advisor. It is intended to provide transparency about the tool’s knowledge base and serve as a standalone resource for residents.

Last updated: June 2026

